<hw>Ground"sel</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>grundswilie</ets>, AS. <ets>grundeswylige</ets>,
<ets>grundeswelge</ets>, earlier <ets>gundiswilge</ets>; <ets>gund</ets>
