a running from the eye. See <er>Swallow</er>, <pos>v.</pos>]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>An annual composite plant (<spn>Senecio
vulgaris</spn>), one of the most common and widely distributed weeds on
the globe.</def></p>

